  <string name="settings_instructions">First-time setup:\n1. Tap \"Enable Keyboard\" and enable LexiSharp Keyboard in system settings\n2. Tap \"Choose Keyboard\" to switch to LexiSharp Keyboard\n3. Grant microphone permission, then long‑press the mic button on the keyboard to try\n\nFor better background service stability, it\'s recommended to grant the following permissions in system settings:\n• Auto-start in background\n• Background running (keep alive)\n• Show pop-up windows while running in the background\n\nThis is an open-source app that guarantees no privacy data will be uploaded.</string>
